data.title: Well worth a visit
data.text: 2 different devices on Sunday, both traditional and contemporary. Plenty of parking, enjoyable music and interesting speakers. Christmas Eve service unbelievable in terms of lighting,music and friendship.

data.title: Great Youth Program
data.text: Pastor Ron Watson gives some thought provoking and entertaining sermons. Trinity has both early and late traditional services and a contemporary service (casual); except during July and August when they have a combined service. The youth program here is outstanding with Sunday school and outside youth activities including summer camp, missions, retreats and fundraising.

data.title: Friendly and open to visitors
data.text: Two service opportunities.  Traditional at 8:15 and 11:00.  Contemporary at 9:30.  Take your pick according to your preference.  Music is outstanding.  Associate pastor, warm and welcoming.  Pastor provides an excellent intelligent sermon.

data.title: A warm welcome to visitors
data.text: Let them know that you are visiting and they will give you coffee mug commemorating your visit. Ron Watson gives some great and entertaining sermons. They have both early and late traditional services and a contemporary service (casual); except during July and August when they have a combined service.
